    # rb "I didn't tell you, but the police actually put me in a room and interrogated me. They thought that I might be involved with the whole meth ring with Mickey."
    rb "No te lo conté, pero la policía me metió en una habitación y me interrogó. Pensaban que podría estar involucrado en todo el chanchullo de la metanfetamina con Mickey."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:58
translate spanish reba12_73152f54:

    # rb "They yelled at me, threatened me... it was scary."
    rb "Me gritaron, me amenazaron... fue aterrador."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:59
translate spanish reba12_89052a8b:

    # pc "I'm sorry. That's awful."
    pc "Lo siento. Eso es horrible."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:60
translate spanish reba12_1f84cfdc:

    # rb "I feel like if I don't get away, I'm going to get caught up in something. Even with Mickey gone, I have other family - cousins, uncles... they're all involved in that stuff."
    rb "Siento que si no me alejo, me voy a ver envuelta en algo. Aunque Mickey ya no esté, tengo otros familiares: primos, tíos... todos están metidos en esas cosas."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:61
translate spanish reba12_021a6b49:

